text: Cynthia Lynne "Cindy" Axne (n√©e: Wadle; born April 20, 1965) is an American business woman and politician. She was the United States Representative for the 3rd Congressional District of Iowa from 2019 until 2023. The district represents the southwest part of Iowa. Axne is a member of the U.S. Democratic Party. Axne was born in Grand Rapids, Michigan. In November 2022, she lost her re-election bid to Zach Nunn. ==References== Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:United States representatives from Iowa Category:1965 births Category:Living people
